Story-

Once upon a time in a forest, there lived a monkey who recided on a berry tree, which was on the bank of the river.
In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife. One day crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested
under the tree. The kind herted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits,
as he loved them. As days passed by, the crocodile and the monkey become good friends. 